MCP server not recognized by Claude <p>Symptoms: - RapidTriage tools don't appear in Claude Desktop - "Server not found" errors in Claude logs - MCP connection failures</p> <p>Solutions: 1. Verify Configuration Path:     <pre><code># Check Claude config location
